su2espr

1. INTRODUCTION
su2espr is a Sketchup plug-in whose aim is to export geometries
representing zones, created within Sketchup, to the geometry description
file used in ESP-r.

su2espr has been developed by Nestor Perez. Issues with su2espr can be
reported at the project's Google Code site, found at
http://code.google.com/p/su2espr. Questions and suggestions can be
directed to nestor.perezrguez [at] google.com

